      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Offered for sale is an exceptional vehicle in absolute mint condition, truly a rare find for the discerning buyer. The exterior is flawless, with original paint that retains a deep, showroom-quality shine and is completely free of scratches, chips, or dings. Inside, the cabin remains in like-new condition, with pristine upholstery and every electronic feature functioning perfectly. Mechanically, this car is impeccable, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no signs of wear. This is a collector-grade example that provides a driving experience indistinguishable from when it first left the dealership.",
