    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This vehicle is ready for someone with a vision and a bit of mechanical know-how! While it currently needs some significant TLC and mechanical attention to get back to its best, it offers a fantastic opportunity for a restoration enthusiast or anyone looking for a budget-friendly parts car. It's a diamond in the rough waiting for the right person to bring it back to life!",
