    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, has been maintained to an exacting standard. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a specimen of unrivaled quality and performance.",
      "price": 47500.0,
